there was nothing more we could do.

272
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:06,560
Néstor may be to blame
for a lot of things,

273
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:08,320
but not your cancer.

274
00:16:17,760 --> 00:16:18,600
Are you okay?

275
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:20,160
