320
00:19:23,200 --> 00:19:26,240
it was a shitty move
not to tell you about Lluís sooner.

321
00:19:26,320 --> 00:19:28,320
So, I'm sorry.

322
00:19:30,640 --> 00:19:33,240
So, in the end,
you and I did have something.

323
00:19:35,520 --> 00:19:39,200
